data.output: Mischa and her family were going to collect their three new puppies. Mischa and her brother Tommy could not wait to see their little faces again. "What are we going to call the puppies?!" the siblings dad asked. "Petrol, Diesel and Pump!" Tommy beamed.

"Thanks for listening and please send your friends to the show!" Ellis said to the audience. Ellis had just completed her first one-woman show of her tour, and the show was called 'A letter to my younger self'. She was so proud of herself, she hadn't let production interfere too much and her personal stamp remained well and truly on the show.

"I dream of having my own cleaning empire someday" Sohail smiled at the panel. He was attending an interview for an internship at Organ NIZE - a professional organising company who visit clients and organise and clean their home, office, or other space for them. "My strengths involve complying with all policies and procedures, following safety regulations, and putting the clients needs first".

The three best friends Erin, Geri and Holly were on their way to their first ever spiritual retreat. "Just going to go do the parking payment" Holly called as the girls got out of the car. "I can't wait to just exist for the next few days at the retreat! No more doom and gloom at work!"  Geri said to Erin.
